              "language": "ckb",
              "text": "لەوانەیە کاتەکە سبەی بێت."
            },
            {
              "language": "en",
              "text": "Maybe the appointment is tomorrow."
            },
            {
              "language": "fa",
              "text": "شاید قرار فردا باشد."
            },
            {
              "language": "kmr",
              "text": "Dibe ku hevdîtin sibê be."
            },
            {
              "language": "pl",
              "text": "Może termin jest jutro."
            },
